DATA CLOUD
Analyze Data from Data Cloud

Data Cloud allows you to use various tools and products to analyze your data.

Unlock Hidden Insights with Tableau
After you’ve combined, unified, and harmonized your data in Data Cloud, it’s now ready for you to analyze. Use Tableau to find useful and actionable insights that can drive business success and create a personalized experience for your customers. Data Cloud, Tableau, and Salesforce 360 apps work together to consolidate your data and create a single customer record. Unlock hidden insights, and make decisions based on all your customer data.
Load Data from Data Cloud into Marketing Cloud Intelligence
Connect Data Cloud to Marketing Cloud Intelligence to analyze your customer data and build dashboards and reports.
Using the JDBC Driver in Data Cloud
The Java Database Connectivity (JDBC) driver allows for a connection to Data Cloud ANSI SQL API. This connection lets you access and retrieve data using your favorite tools that are supported by JDBC.
Gain Insights on Data with CRM Analytics
Data Cloud allows you to perform exploratory analysis on your data at different stages of its lifecycle using CRM Analytics. You can build contextual insights and create interactive views on a data lake object (DLO), data model object (DMO), or calculated insights object (CIO) without loading the data into CRM Analytics. You can filter the Data Cloud data, drill deeper, and act on the data directly from the dashboards.
Data Cloud Reports and Dashboards
Easily create standard reports on single or multiple related data model objects (DMOs) or Calculated Insights to determine which areas of your business to focus on. Or, build a custom report type on DMOs to get information on the most pertinent fields and records from Data Cloud. You can group, filter, and summarize records in the report, run it for near real-time information and share it with others. And, make business decisions faster by visualizing KPIs and trends from Data Cloud reports in your dashboards.
Segment Intelligence in Data Cloud
Segment Intelligence is a data-driven app that empowers customers to better use existing segments and increase the impact of their marketing activity. Segment Intelligence combines Data Cloud and CRM Analytics to surface insights on segments across multiple channels, engagement types, and conversion sources, such as revenue from Commerce Cloud. Build and enhance segments with actionable performance insights and improve your marketing return on investment (ROI) with more relevant audiences and campaigns.
